  "text": "The lesion scores the mucosal lesions were quantified by the scoring system (0 À5) 0 = no damage, 1 = Local edema and inflammation without ulcers; 2 = One ulcer without inflammation; 3 = one to two ulcers with inflammation & lesion diameter < 1 cm; 4 = More than two ulcers with lesion diameter 1-2 cm; 5 = Sever ulceration with lesion diameter > 2 cm [CITATION_1] .",
